OL,5,G1915 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FSouth Africa v Canada (Kick-off
OL,7,     F8.00pm). Coverage of the opening
OL,8,     Fround-of-32 match, which comes
OL,9,     Ffrom Los Angeles Stadium in
OL,10,     FInglewood, USA. After a mammoth
OL,11,     Fgroup stage consisting of 72
OL,12,     Fgames, only 16 of the 48 teams
OL,13,     Fhave been eliminated, with 32
OL,14,     Fnations taking part in the
OL,15,     Fknockout stage for the first time
OL,16,     Fin World Cup history. Co-hosts
OL,17,     FCanada finished second in Group B
OL,18,     Fto progress to the knockout stages
OL,19,     Ffor the first time in their
OL,20,     Fhistory, despite losing 2-1 to
OL,21,     FSwitzerland in their final group
OL,22,     Fmatch on Wednesday. South Africa
